              "eventid": "valueChanged",
              "script": "\tproviderName \u003d tagPath[tagPath.find(\"[\")+1:tagPath.find(\"]\")]\n\tif providerName !\u003d currentValue.value:\n\t\tsystem.tag.writeBlocking(\"[.]TagProvider\", providerName)"
